		{"id":"b9680e950e527d66","type":"text","text":"permission slips for creation.\n\nlet me remind you why you bought your guitar, why you drew as a child\n\na permission slip for creation sliding up into your screen as your scroll up\n\nthe scrolling up motion itself turns into a cool animation feeling of bounce, of the thing scrolling  up into the screen, and bouncing back down. ","x":-288,"y":-303,"width":348,"height":223},
		{"id":"7ddd02e941a07499","type":"text","text":"a way to help think about painting in 3d is to paint some 3d things! hold your brush at that angle and really feel it painting around the object, on its sides, feel that change in plane in space on the page","x":25,"y":50,"width":250,"height":250}
